<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Fantasy Creatures Art Museum</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #111;
            color: #eee;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header {
            background: #222;
            padding: 30px;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: #7fd4ff;
        }

        .gallery {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 30px;
        }

        .art-piece {
            background: #1a1a1a;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 900px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
        }

        img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #7fd4ff;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #ddd;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #222;
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>Fantasy Creatures Art Museum</header>

<div class="gallery">

    <div class="art-piece">
        <img src="Forest Guardian Spirit.jpg" alt="Forest Guardian Spirit">
        <h2>Forest Guardian Spirit</h2>
        <p>A mystical protector formed from leaves, vines, and ancient woodland energy. This guardian watches over the forest with quiet wisdom.</p>
        <p><strong>Created with:</strong> AI Generative Art Tool</p>
    </div>

    <div class="art-piece">
        <img src="Crystal Dragon.png" alt="Crystal Dragon">
        <h2>Crystal Dragon</h2>
        <p>A majestic dragon with shimmering crystal scales that refract light into dazzling colors. A rare and powerful creature of legend.</p>
        <p><strong>Created with:</strong> AI Generative Art Tool</p>
    </div>

    <div class="art-piece">
        <img src="Shadow Panther.jpeg" alt="Shadow Panther">
        <h2>Shadow Panther</h2>
        <p>A sleek, enchanted panther born from living shadow. Its glowing eyes pierce the darkness as it moves silently through the night.</p>
        <p><strong>Created with:</strong> AI Generative Art Tool</p>
    </div>

    <div class="art-piece">
        <img src="Moonlight Kitsune.png" alt="Moonlight Kitsune">
        <h2>Moonlight Kitsune</h2>
        <p>A mystical fox spirit illuminated by moonlight, with flowing fur and ethereal energy radiating from its many tails.</p>
        <p><strong>Created with:</strong> AI Generative Art Tool</p>
    </div>

</div>

<footer>
    © 2026 Fantasy Creatures Art Museum — Created by Nevaeh
</footer>

</body>
</html>
